Series of commits in gssapi removed important functions necessary
for libgsscred.so in /on-default/usr/src/cmd/gss/gsscred/.

Use k5-der.h in GSS library
Remove the DER implementations in lib/gssapi and use k5-der.h instead.
https://github.com/krb5/krb5/commit/fdceb225f881e2b1337eebcb9a9443fa4a9be3fd

There is a new header reimplementing the same functionality. Functions are not
exported.

Add a simple DER support header
https://github.com/krb5/krb5/commit/548da160b52b25a106e9f6077d6a42c2c049586c

This patch comes with wrappers libgsscred can link against. This patch is not
suitable for upstream.

